Help on skill: repair weapon
Skill type: neutral
Usage duration: 10

With this skill you can repair the damage inflicted on your weapon.
The worse the condition of the weapon or shield, the more
difficult it is to repair, meaning it will take several
shots and thus more time.

Using this skill removes the effect of skill 'sharpen'.
Your skill percent affects how much the condition of a weapon
or a shield will restore.

